            <abstract>
              <p>This document, part of the document number 6 in Carlo Conti Rossini's edition, part II of CCR 6 according to Alessandro Bausi's system of reference.
              While there are reasons to consider part I and part II of CCR 6 according to Bausi's system of reference as two parts one document, here they are treated as two documents on the basis of codicoloical disposition and mise en texte.
According to Contri Rossini, the handwriting of this document is the same as in <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6311CCR6">Lālibalā's gʷǝlt to the church of Masqal and to the church of Mary</ref>.
                  This document is known only from Conti Rossini's publication.
</p>

